*Prva* sezona serije je bila najbolja. (The first season of the series was the best.)

*Prvom* koraku sledi drugi. (The second follows the first step.)

*Prvo* je pitanje bilo veoma teško. (The first question was very difficult.)

*Prve* snove treba čuvati. (The first dreams should be kept.)

*Prvih* nekoliko minuta bilo je nezaboravno. (The first few minutes were unforgettable.)

*Prvu* rečenicu sam napisao u tri sekunde. (I wrote the first sentence in three seconds.)